summary: I WAS IN AN ACCIDENT IN MY 2000 VOLVO S70 IN WHICH THE CAR WAS TOTALED.  THE DRIVER'S SIDE AIRBAG DID NOT DEPLOY.  THE PASSENGER SIDE AIRBAG DID DEPLOY.  ALTHOUGH, I WAS NOT SERIOUSLY INJURED, I WOULD LIKE TO REPORT THAT THE DRIVER'S SIDE AIRBAG DID NOT DEPLOY AT ANY TIME DURING THE ACCIDENT.
